 {\"sentence\": \"The questions.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The questions\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quizzical brows.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The quizzical brows\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lightbulb moments.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lightbulb moments\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the range of expressions, from bemusement to wonder to the shaking of heads.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And the range\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"expressions\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"bemusement\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"the shaking\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll often get in an Uber, and the driver will ask if she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s an athlete.Yes.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"an Uber\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the driver\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes she says no to end the conversation.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If not, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll ask about the sport.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her answers range from \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctrack and field\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ca field athlete\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to the one that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s certain to provoke more questions.I compete in steeplechase.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctrack\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"field\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ca field\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"more questions\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"steeplechase\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When they don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll explain: it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a race, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s long and there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lot of running.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s long\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while running, there are barriers to surmount, and those barriers aren\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t like normal hurdles.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"barriers\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"those barriers\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"normal hurdles\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are water pits to navigate.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"water pits\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitors fall regularly\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and often spectacularly.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou have to be some sort of stupid to try and do this thing at all,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"this thing\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She laughs, then, when one of track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most popular debates begins.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"most popular debates\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the hardest event?\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest event\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many say the 800-meter run, because it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a nearly full sprint for two laps around a track.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 800-meter run\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"two laps\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"a track\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some say the 1,500-meters, because it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same thing, but not as close to full speed throughout and yet also twice as long.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-meters\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"full speed\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quigley would like to add steeplechase to the debate.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9961032533001633e-24, \"text\": \"Quigley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"steeplechase\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But perhaps it shouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be an argument at all.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an argument\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her sport requires elite endurance, for all those meters that must be run.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her sport\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"elite endurance\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"all those meters\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitors must be athletic, to go over the barriers; physically tough, to withstand inevitable pain; mentally fortified, to focus while still doing everything else.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"the barriers\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"inevitable pain\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Otherwise, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll land in photographs that live forever: bodies upside down, heads about to hit both water and track.\\u00c2 This race is one of track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most unpredictable, most strategic and least understood.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll land\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"photographs\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"bodies\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"both water\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"This race\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For fans ofOlympic competition, extreme sport enthusiasts or anyone who simply loves watching anything crash, steeplechase is the sport for you.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"ofOlympic competition\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme sport enthusiasts\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"anything crash\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"steeplechase\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s time to Embrace the Chase, where track meets distance running meets pile-ups in car accidents meets Game of Thrones-level masochism.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2168, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chase\", \"score\": 0.6402572724235441, \"rank\": 0.40535497451283453, \"text\": \"Chase\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chase\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chase\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s time\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"distance\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"pile-ups\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"car accidents\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"Game\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"Thrones-level masochism\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First, to properly embrace, understand the basics: 3,000 meters to run, five barriers to get over and the water pit to survive.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the basics\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"3,000 meters\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"five barriers\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"the water pit\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The running unfolds on seven-and-1/2 laps on the track.\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The running\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"seven-and-1/2 laps\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes must gooverall barriers; failure on any one means automatic disqualification.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"barriers\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"failure\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"any one\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"automatic disqualification\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On lap 1, competitors skip the water and the first barrier, which is wider than the others, owing to the propensity of participants to stay bunched together early into races.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lap\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"the first barrier\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"the propensity\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Imagine leaping over one while next to other racers, all wearing track spikes.)\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Imagine\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"other racers\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"track spikes\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After lap 1, no obstacles are skipped, which adds up to seven water leaps and 28 barriers to jump over.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lap\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"no obstacles\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"seven water leaps\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"28 barriers\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pit runs 12 feet near the end of the track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094its width: nearly 2.3 feet; its depth: 28 inches, at the deepest point\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094where it curves before the backstretch.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pit\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2947}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094its width\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 2.3 feet\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"28 inches\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3011}, {\"ngram\": \"the deepest point\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094where\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"the backstretch\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re located either inside Lane 1 or outside the last lane (often 8 or 9).\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"Lane\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the last lane\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a hurdle in front of the pit, although calling that monstrosity a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009churdle\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d fails to capture its essence.\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hurdle\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"the pit\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"that monstrosity\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009churdle\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"its essence\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Think: a hurdle that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s more sturdy, that won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t fall if anyone collides with it, and that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s wider than more \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cnormal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d versions.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hurdle\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"that won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t fall\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"more \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cnormal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d versions\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That bad boy stretches 12 feet in width.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That bad boy\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"12 feet\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"width\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s strategy, for sure, especially around the water pits.\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s strategy\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"the water pits\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitors most often step up, on top of the barrier, then leap as far as they can.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the barrier\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without full running momentum, though, they don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t usually clear the water pit.\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full running momentum\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"the water pit\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The general rule for an ideal sequence of steps ends with one foot in the water and the other out.\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The general rule\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"an ideal sequence\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"steps\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"one foot\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who rely more on momentum jump over the barrier and stride through the water, which means they get far more than wet.\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"momentum jump\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"the barrier\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"stride\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With so many other competitors, everything\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094gets wetter and wetter as the race unspools.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many other competitors\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3937}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094gets wetter\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3978}, {\"ngram\": \"wetter\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3989}, {\"ngram\": \"the race unspools\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This turns steeplechase into something more likeWipeout.\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe an athlete slips on a barrier.\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4085}, {\"ngram\": \"a barrier\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe they land off-balance.\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"off-balance\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe they somersault forward.\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe they land\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094on one foot, body bent at a horizontal angle or, in the worst case,headfirst.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one foot\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"body\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4201}, {\"ngram\": \"a horizontal angle\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst case\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe the temperatures are lower that day, making the water seeping through their shoes and socks less of an annoyance and more of a menace.\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the temperatures\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"their shoes\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4349}, {\"ngram\": \"an annoyance\", \"from\": 4368, \"to\": 4380}, {\"ngram\": \"a menace\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe their shoes slip and slide.\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their shoes\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"slide\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They still must continue running and surmounting.\\u00c2 Let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s run through the typical